window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Tav and his allies have a new and unwelcome neighbor: A rogue unit of murderous National Guard who intend to take control of the area, its resources, and its people for themselves. Assaulting even a small military base is no mean feat, so Tav will have to train his girls to be weapons of war in addition to just survivors.</p> <p>The Guards are unable to live in peace, so Tav must prepare for war.</p>"; 
